{"tid":723131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"游蕙禎出獄後首開腔稱搵工要緊　望「帶住過去經驗繼續行」","createTime":"2018-06-30T06:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-30T17:31:05.000Z","uid":20933,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0b1cb602da6fa7f06a2d19828499055bb33170c3","tid":723131,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T06:47:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180630/large/1530335157_e822.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180630%2Flarge%2F1530335157_e822.jpg&h=647f5067&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180630/large/1530335964_d2e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180630%2Flarge%2F1530335964_d2e6.jpg&h=2e88b8b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n游蕙禎在朋友陪同下，到超市買日用品。(金敏琍攝)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180630/large/1530339215_6092.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180630%2Flarge%2F1530339215_6092.jpg&h=db0eb68a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"73ea5eb4fd26b1262d3102cac097dba1ebf75435","tid":723131,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T06:47:29.000Z","msg":"吃過午餐後，中午12時50分左右，游蕙禎離開酒店，只見她薄施脂粉，白色上衣配黑色短裙，精神奕奕。她首度開腔談及坐監感受，與及未來計劃。記者問她有否重生的感覺，她說：「唔可以叫『重生』，唯有帶住過去既經驗繼續行。」<br />\n<br />\n4星期的牢獄生涯，令游蕙禎感受深刻。她說：「裡面(監獄)感覺好靜好有規律，同外面感覺好唔同，畀我可以諗到多啲嘢。」她坦言，目前以生計為首要任務，「出嚟首先係要穩定番收入，搵番份工，任何人都需要生活。」至於明天會否參與7.1遊行，是否繼續從政？她未有具體答覆：「好多私人嘢要處理咗先，要睇吓...咁7.1都係一個表達途徑。」<br />\n<br />\n本來已經纖瘦的游蕙禎，似乎再瘦一圈。較早前戰友為她買來至愛的炸雞做午餐，不過她表示其實沒有特別的食物想吃，又指會休息一會，「好攰，晏啲會探父母。」隨即登上私家車離開。"},{"pid":"d094c537813d394365d5a8846230be60e486f2b2","tid":723131,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T06:47:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180630/58382928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180630%2F58382928&d=q37Okwz3dMy7n%2BC1cFV2dy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=3389b6ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180630%2F58382928&h=5671416f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180630/58382928</a>"},{"pid":"b053bb6545c1584cb5b4b05d4adf4d7493ab5af7","tid":723131,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T06:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 短裙仔"},{"pid":"b03a1a6e99076e1b663d1cad5fd31c9b80cc5e41","tid":723131,"uid":65887,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T06:49:43.000Z","msg":"搵連登仔埋單未得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07592e363c3a1fa4a96d9ab5cdd804116479b677","tid":723131,"uid":17008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T06:49:59.000Z","msg":"出獄送炸雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b21a15cc51e231bf429a84f58e38fb58279150","tid":723131,"uid":112551,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T06:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩完啦，都唔知有無公司肯請，請左又驚外部壓力．　"},{"pid":"d5c7ce1a445b05f00546ae783a4c2151a60fab50","tid":723131,"uid":17008,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T06:51:11.000Z","msg":"佢條仔應該等左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c83df68278dfccd5f6b671b0069ca1124de29d","tid":723131,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-30T06:53:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb8c3887714